{"tid":1259063,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話杯葛係小學雞，小朋友","createTime":"2019-06-26T12:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T12:30:44.000Z","uid":264246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75eb0acbec9f6df78aa9456e34f2711039fa2232","tid":1259063,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"由上一次雨傘開始已經一堆人話杯葛警察，杯葛親中係小學雞行為，每次講親都會有人答:仲細呀?（當然當中應該有警犬驚俾人杯）<br />\n但係當最低成本既行為大家都唔肯做，而更進一步既亦都相信你地唔會做<br />\n所以希望你地起碼攬番最基本果份野做，杯葛警犬，撐中人士，唔係親中機構消費，拎哂中資銀行既錢出黎，盡量做好自己果份<br />\n可以唔需要你地企出黎，但需要你地幫手消佢地既氣焰，等佢地知道做既野有代價，同埋會軟化佢地既行為"},{"pid":"55da9f488be32ac94e79bce362d5c127d05c7b70","tid":1259063,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"狗唔會有做人嘅骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［置頂］今晚八點 中環愛丁堡廣場見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n［突發］中環要人！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258994</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"6730d01df4c563097e1621ba1b913aed22ec5cfe","tid":1259063,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b7f78ccf7a5ef6e0b0c20bbc4d7adace658692","tid":1259063,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}